title.text: Martyn Enkelaar is attending Asian Light & Food Festival at Dok Amsterdam.

message.text:
>> www.asianlightfestival.nl
Asian Light & Food Festival 
 << (January + February 2024) Do you love Asian food? Asian light and food festival
Visit the Asian Light & Food Festival in Wormerveer in February this year. The winter season takes place in winter and winter takes place in Amsterdam. A lot of things have happened in the past in recent years, and a lot of things have happened in the past.

We have made a lot of music in recent years and we want to show you some talent in the karaoke field. Trommel offers tickets for families and friends via www.asianlightfestival.nl.
🎏🎤🍤
@iedereen

FRAUD WARNING
There are many frauds active in housing groups. 
Never pay without a viewing in person and a check that the landlord is real. Do not believe stories about the landlord or other renters not being present in the country, foreign bank accounts and communication by whatsapp or e-mail. Realize that photos, contract and even identity papers can be stolen from the Internet.
https://www.facebook.com/groups/DutchHousingExperience/?ref=share
